Package: worldfootballR
Type: Package
Title: An R Package to Extract World Football (Soccer) Data from Fbref.com, transfermarkt.com and understat.com
Version: 0.4.2
Authors@R: c(person("Jason Zivkovic", email = "jase.ziv83@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre")),
           person("Tony ElHabr", email = "anthonyelhabr@gmail.com",
                  role = "ctb"))
URL: https://github.com/JaseZiv/worldfootballR
BugReports: https://github.com/JaseZiv/worldfootballR/issues
Description: This R package will enable users to extract a number of different game and player statistics and metrics from numerous football sites, including fbref.com, transfer data from transfermarket.com and shooting data from understat.com.
